pull_request_template.md
# Pull Request

## Description
Please include a summary of the change or the feature you're introducing. Link to any relevant issues or discussions.

## Type of Change
- [ ] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)
- [ ] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)
- [ ] Breaking change (fix or feature that would cause existing functionality to not work as expected)
- [ ] This change requires a documentation update

## How Has This Been Tested?
Describe how you've tested your changes. If applicable, mention any specific tests that should be run.

## Checklist:
- [ ] My code follows the project's coding standards.
- [ ] I have documented my code, particularly in areas that are complex.
- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation.
- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works.
- [ ] Any dependent changes have been merged and published in downstream modules.

## Additional Information
Include any additional information or screenshots that would assist in the review of this PR.

